{"tid":976462,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【騰訊無份】內地遊戲審批再解凍　第2輪共批84款遊戲","createTime":"2019-01-10T11:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T14:54:03.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bcaad1a5c3685d29f234870e22d7cfbb8eee4567","tid":976462,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2305569/org/ebb5c777a3c726a24c80dedb3f1144d4.jpg/6sn0-BF_ks0wSY8KdagkOVREKneXozE6mjnsRpo57EY?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2305569%2Forg%2Febb5c777a3c726a24c80dedb3f1144d4.jpg%2F6sn0-BF_ks0wSY8KdagkOVREKneXozE6mjnsRpo57EY%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=9b67d413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地時隔9個月重啟遊戲審批，繼上月公布有80款遊戲獲批後，國家新聞出版廣電總局官網再公布2018年12月份國產網絡遊戲審批信息，新增84款遊戲在12月取得遊戲版號，名單上仍未見騰訊（0700）及網易旗下遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n 騰訊最新跌0.49%，報326元，成交17.45億元。<br />\n<br />\n廣電總局昨日公布獲批的84款遊戲中，有83款為手機遊戲，包括三七互娛的《神魔血脈》、掌趣科技的《冷械島》以及百度旗下公司的《新三生三世十里桃花》等，審批時間為2018年12月29日，上輪批出80款遊戲的審批時間則為2018年12月19日。<br />\n<br />\n兩輪審批中小型遊戲廠商為主<br />\n<br />\n《新京報》報道，廣電總局兩次遊戲審批均以中小型遊戲廠商為主，半個月內兩次公布遊戲版號名單，業內人士認為是遊戲版號審批正常化的信號，而與過去每月批出700個版號比較，已見當局的遊戲總量調控。<br />\n<br />\n去年內地暫停遊戲審批，導致騰訊等科企的收入受壓，市場亦對遊戲行業轉趨審慎。中宣部版權局副局長馮士新去年出席中國遊戲產業年會時透露，當局已完成審核首批部分遊戲，正在準備核發版號，惟因申報遊戲的存量較大，故仍需要一段時間。"},{"pid":"7100c476f99a6fdd55b0fa0936bb5f29e815dfdf","tid":976462,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"無份聽日照升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e06b25f460880719ab510e302f9ff66f4af01c8","tid":976462,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"馬雲係黨員<br />\n馬化騰唔係,好明顯了"},{"pid":"e80fe80c843b8cd45d23fd5a9a9a852e2192772b","tid":976462,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:14:43.000Z","msg":"騰訊咪咁撚孤寒<br />\n上面要幾多好心你照俾啦<br />\n小財唔出大財唔入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb5554b0b7647592c6ca720b16c3061509e79c2","tid":976462,"uid":55023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"照升 易幻發"},{"pid":"43eb884b7d7bebae85a16f0c8408246abe13e342","tid":976462,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb5554b0b7647592c6ca720b16c3061509e79c2","tid":976462,"uid":55023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"照升 易幻發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005cd56803ea1e51b34bcb24afddb3a6fd9dc595","tid":976462,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7100c476f99a6fdd55b0fa0936bb5f29e815dfdf","tid":976462,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"無份聽日照升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"今朝新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa34271472c63f42b1f80e2efe1a9d2267c9567","tid":976462,"uid":227000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"Rainbow six <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b86d066d150dc6808f4294efd7577c68465c63","tid":976462,"uid":227000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fa34271472c63f42b1f80e2efe1a9d2267c9567","tid":976462,"uid":227000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"Rainbow six <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"屌 望撚錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}